Crowdfunding Tip:If you have friends who have thousands of followers in social media sites, ask them to link your #crowdfunding campaign.
Crowdfunding Tip:Do you have friends who own a blog or website? Try to ask them to put a link to your #crowdfunding campaign.
Crowdfunding Tip:Don't be shy. Start your own Facebook Page or Google+ Page, then post and share your #crowdfunding campaign to the world.
Crowdfunding Tip: Upload photos and real images to your campaign. A video would also make your #crowdfunding campaign reliable.
